metadata.name: Lessons In Love - The Collection
metadata.description:
This collection is from the heart. For those who this resonates with, I want you to know there is healing at the end of your journey. We all make mistakes in love, but through introspection, we gain the biggest lessons; we grow. 

I hope this collection will walk you through my process of learning and show you the strength that comes from the other side of heartbreak. 

[Poem Index]  
Introspection - 00:20  
When Butterflies Fade & Reality Sets In - 1:01  
When Love is a Rollercoaster - 2:13  
You Can't Run Forever - 3:06  
Navigating Through Lessons Learned in Love - 4:23
